{"word":"G1231 - διαγινώσκω - diaginṓskō - dee-ag-in-o'-sko - Enquire","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">διαγινώσκω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">diaginṓskō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">dee-ag-in-o'-sko</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Enquire</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - திட்டமாய் விசாரி"},{"paragraph":"to distinguish, in a legal sense, to examine, determine, decide,"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1223 - διά - diá - dee-ah'/1223\">G1223</a> and <a href=\"#/G1097 - γινώσκω - ginṓskō - ghin-oce'-ko/1097\">G1097</a>; to <i>know thoroughly</i>, that is, <i>ascertain exactly:</i> - (would) enquire, know the uttermost.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}